quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  37,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  37,1,qitaar Dur qitaar saf bandhnay walon ki qasam
  37,2,phir unn ki qasam jo dantnay phatkarnaywalay hain
  37,3,phir unn ki qasam jo kalaam nasiyaat sunanay walay hain
  37,4,tumhara mabood haqeeqi bas aik hi hai
  37,5,"woh jo zameen aur asmano ka aur tamam unn cheezon ka maalik hai jo zameen o aasman mein hain, aur saaray mashriqon ka maalik"
  37,6,hum ne aasman duniya ko taron ki zeenat se aaraasta kya hai
  37,7,aur har shetan sarkash se is ko mehfooz kar diya hai
  37,8,"yeh shyatin malay aala ki baatein nahi sun satke, har taraf se maaray aur hankay jatay hain"
  37,9,aur un ke liye pihm azaab hai
  37,10,taham agar koi un mein se kuch le uray to aik taiz shola is ka peecha karta hai
  37,11,"ab inn se pucho, inn ki paidaiesh ziyada mushkil hai ya unn cheezon ki jo hum ne peda kar rakhi hain? inn ko to hum ne lais daar gaaray se peda kya hai"
  37,12,tum ( Allah ki qudrat ke karishmo par ) heran ho aur yeh is ka mazaq ura rahay hain
  37,13,samjhaya jata hai to samajh kar nahi dete
  37,14,koi nishani dekhte hain to usay tethon mein uratay hain
  37,15,"aur kehte hain"" yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai"
  37,16,bhala kahin aisa ho sakta hai ke jab hum mar chuke hon aur matti ban jayen aur hadion ka panjar reh jayen uss waqt hum phir zindah kar ke utha kharray kiye jayen ?
  37,17,"aur kya hamaray aglay waqton ke aaba o ajdaad bhi uthaye jayen ge? """
  37,18,"inn se kaho haan, aur tum ( khuda ke muqablay mein ) be bas ho"
  37,19,bas aik hi jhirki ho gi aur yakayak yeh apni aankhon se ( woh sab kuch jis ki khabar di ja rahi hai ) dekh rahay hon ge
  37,20,"uss waqt yeh kahin ge"" haae hamari kam bakhti, yeh to yom ul jaza hai """
  37,21,""" yeh wohi faislay ka din hai jisay tum jhtlaya karte thay """
  37,22,( hukum ho ga ) ghair lao sab zaalmon aur un ke sathiyon aur unn mabodon ko jin ki woh khuda ko chore kar bandagi kya karte thay
  37,23,phir un sab ko jahannum ka rasta dikhao
  37,24,"aur zara aِnhintehraؤ, inn se kuch poochna hai"
  37,25,""" kya ho gaya tumhe, ab kyun aik dosray ki madad nahi karte ?"
  37,26,"arrey, aaj to yeh apne aap ko ( aur aik dosray ko ) hawalay kiye day rahay hain! """
  37,27,is ke baad yeh aik dosray ki taraf murrain ge aur baahum takraar shuru kar den ge
  37,28,"( pairwi karne walay apne pishwaon se ) kahin ge,"" tum hamaray paas seedhay rukh se atay thay """
  37,29,"woh jawab den ge,"" nahi balkay tum khud imaan laane walay nah thay"
  37,30,"hamara tum par koi zor nah tha, tum khud hi sarkash log thay"
  37,31,aakhir kaar hum apne rab ke iss farmaan ke mustahiq ho gay ke hum azaab ka maza chakhnay walay hain
  37,32,"so hum ne tum ko b_hka ya, hum khud behke hue thay """
  37,33,iss terhan woh sab uss roz azaab mein mushtarik hon ge
  37,34,hum mujrimon ke sath yahi kuch kya karte hain
  37,35,"yeh woh log thay ke jab un se kaha jata"" Allah ke siwa koi mabood Bar haq nahi hai"" to yeh ghamand mein aa jatay thay"
  37,36,"aur kehte thay"" kya hum aik shayar Majnoon ki khatir apne mabodon ko chore den? """
  37,37,halaank woh haq le kar aaya tha aur is ne Rasolo-n ki tasdeeq ki thi
  37,38,( ab un se kaha jaye ga ke ) tum laziman dard naak saza ka maza chakhnay walay ho
  37,39,aur tumhe jo badla bhi diya ja raha hai aُnhi aamaal ka diya ja raha hai jo tum karte rahay ho
  37,40,magar Allah ke cheeda bande ( is injaam bad se ) mehfooz hon ge
  37,41,un ke liye jana boojha rizaq hai
  37,42,"har terhan ki lazeez cheeze ,"
  37,43,aur Nemat bhari jannaten
  37,44,jin mein woh izzat ke sath rakhay jayen ge takhton par aamnay samnay bathain ge
  37,45,sharaab ke chashmo se saghar bhar bhar kar un ke darmain phira-ay jayen ge
  37,46,"chamakti hui sharaab, jo peenay walon ke liye lazat ho gi"
  37,47,nah un ke jism ko is se koi zarrar hoga aur nah un ki aqal is se kharab ho gi
  37,48,"aur un ke paas nigehain bachanay wali, khobsorat aankhon wali aurtain hon gi"
  37,49,aisi naazuk jaisay anday ke chilkay ke neechay chhupi hui jhilli
  37,50,phir woh aik dosray ki taraf mutwajjah ho kar halaat poucheen ge
  37,51,"un mein se aik kahe ga,"" duniya mein mera aik hum nasheen tha"
  37,52,"jo mujh se kaha karta tha, kya tum bhi tasdeeq karne walon mein se ho ?"
  37,53,kya waqai jab hum mar chuke hon ge aur matti ho jayen ge aur hadion ka panjar ban kar reh jayen ge to hamein jaza o saza di jaye gi ?
  37,54,"ab kya aap log dekhna chahtay hain ke woh sahib ab kahan hain? """
  37,55,yeh keh kar jounhi woh jhuke ga to jahannum ki geherai mein is ko dekh le ga
  37,56,"aur is se khitaab kar ke kahe ga"" khuda ki qasam, too to mujhe tabah hi kar dainay wala tha"
  37,57,mere rab ka fazl shaamil haal nah hota to aaj mein bhi unn logon mein se hota jo pakdae hue aeye hain
  37,58,acha to kya ab hum marnay walay nahi hain ?
  37,59,"mout jo hamein aani thi woh bas pehlay aa chuki? ab hamein koi azaab nahi hona? """
  37,60,yaqeenan yahi azeem al shan kamyabi hai
  37,61,aisi hi kamyabi ke liye amal karne walon ko amal karna chahiye
  37,62,"balow, yeh ziyafat achi hai ya zarqomka darakht ?"
  37,63,hum ne uss darakht ko zaalmon ke liye fitnah bana diya hai
  37,64,woh aik darakht hai jo jahannum ki teh se nikalta hai
  37,65,uss ke shagofay aisay hain jaisay shaitano ke sir
  37,66,jahannum ke log ussay khayen ge aur isi se pait bharain ge
  37,67,phir is par peenay ke liye kholta howa pani miley ga
  37,68,aur is ke baad un ki wapsi usi aatish dozakh ki taraf ho gi
  37,69,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne baap dada ko gumraah paaya
  37,70,aur unhi ke naqsh qadam par daud chalay
  37,71,halaank un se pehlay bohat se log gumraah ho chuke thay
  37,72,aur unn mein hum ne tanbeeh karne walay rasool beje thay
  37,73,ab dekh lau ke unn tanbeeh kiye jaane walon ka kya injaam howa
  37,74,is bad anjaami se bas Allah ke wohi bande bachay hain jinhein is ne apne liye khalis kar liya hai
  37,75,"hum ko ( iss se pehlay ) Nooh ne puraka tha, to dekho ke hum kaisay achay jawab dainay walay thay"
  37,76,hum ne uss ko aur is ke ghar walon ko karb azeem se bacha liya
  37,77,aur isi ki nasal ko baqi rakha
  37,78,aur baad ki naslon mein is ki tareef o tauseef chore di
  37,79,salam hai Nooh par tamam duniya walon mein
  37,80,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza diya karte hain
  37,81,Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
  37,82,phir dosray giroh ko hum ne ghark kar diya
  37,83,aur Nooh hi ke tareeqay par chalne wala ibrahim tha
  37,84,jab woh apne rab ke huzoor qalb Saleem le kar aaya
  37,85,"jab uss ne apne baap aur apni qoum se kaha"" yeh kya cheeze hain jin ki tum ibadat kar rahay ho ?"
  37,86,kya Allah ko chore kar jhoot gharrey hue mabood chahtay ho ?
  37,87,"aakhir Allah Rab alaalmin ke baray mein tumhara kya gumaan hai? """
  37,88,phir is ne taron par aik nigah daali
  37,89,aur kaha meri tabiyat kharab hai
  37,90,chunancha woh log usay chore kar chalay gay
  37,91,"unn ke peechay woh chupkay se unn ke mabodon ke mandir mein ghis gaya aur bola"" aap log khatay kyun nahi hain ?"
  37,92,"kya ho gaya, aap log boltay bhi nahi? """
  37,93,is ke baad woh unn par pal para aur seedhay haath se khoob zrbin lagayen
  37,94,( wapas aa kar ) woh log bhage bhage is ke paas aeye
  37,95,"is ne kaha"" kya tum apni hi tarashi hui cheezon ko pujte ho ?"
  37,96,"halaank Allah hi ne tum ko bhi peda kya hai aur unn cheezon ko bhi jinhein tum banatay ho """
  37,97,"unhon ne aapas mein kaha"" is ke liye aik alaao tayyar karo aur usay dehakti hui aag ke dhair mein pheink do """
  37,98,"unhon ne is ke khilaaf aik karwai karni chahi thi, magar hum ne unhi ko neecha dikha diya"
  37,99,"ibrahim ne kaha"" mein apne rab ki taraf jata hon, wohi meri rahnumai kere ga"
  37,100,"ae parwar-digaar, mujhe aik beta ataa kar jo salhonmein se ho """
  37,101,( is dua ke jawab mein ) hum ne is ko aik Haleem ( Burdbar ) larke ki basharat di
  37,102,"woh larka jab is ke sath daud dhoop karne ki Umar ko poanch gaya to ( aik roz ) ibrahim ne is se kaha,"" beta, mein khawab mein daikhta hon ke mein tujhe zibah kar raha hon, ab to bta, tera kya khayaal hai ?"" uss ne kaha,"" abba jaan, jo kuch aap ko hukum diya ja raha hai usay kar dalie, aap Insha Allah mujhe sabroo-n mein se payen ge """
  37,103,aakhir ko jab inn dono ne sir tasleem khham kar diya aur ibrahim ne betay ko maathay ke bil gira diya
  37,104,"aur hum ne nida di ke"" ae ibrahim"
  37,105,to ne khawab sach kar dekhaya hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  37,106,"yaqeenan yeh aik khuli azmaish thi """
  37,107,aur hum ne aik barri qurbani fidyay mein day kar is bachay ko churra liya
  37,108,aur is ki tareef o tauseef hamesha ke liye baad ki naslon mein chore di
  37,109,salam hai ibrahim par
  37,110,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  37,111,yaqeenan woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
  37,112,"aur hum ne usay ishaq ki basharat di, aik nabi salheen mein se"
  37,113,aur usay aur ishaq ko barket di ab un dono ki zaryat mein se koi mohsin hai aur koi apne nafs par Sarih zulm karne wala hai
  37,114,aur hum ne moose o haroon par ahsaan kya
  37,115,unn ko aur un ki qoum ko karb azeem se nijaat di
  37,116,unhen nusrat bakhsh jis ki wajah se wohi ghalib rahay
  37,117,un ko nihayat wazeh kitaab ataa ki
  37,118,inhen raah raast dikhayi
  37,119,aur baad ki naslon mein un ka zikar kher baqi rakha
  37,120,salam hai moose aur haroon par
  37,121,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  37,122,Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray momin bundon mein se thay
  37,123,aur ilyas bhi yaqeenan mursaleen mein se tha
  37,124,"yaad karo jab is ne apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" tum log drtay nahi ho ?"
  37,125,kya tum b - al ko pkarte ho aur Ahsen ul Khalqeen ko chore dete ho
  37,126,"uss Allah ko jo tumhara aur tumahray aglay pichlle aaba o ajdaad ka rab hai? """
  37,127,"magar unhon ne usay jhutla diya, so ab yaqeenan woh saza ke liye paish kiye jaane walay hain"
  37,128,bajuz unn bandgaan khuda ke jin ko khalis kar liya gaya tha
  37,129,aur ilyas ka zikar kher hum ne baad ki naslon mein baqi rakha
  37,130,salam hai ilyas par
  37,131,hum neki karne walon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  37,132,waqai woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
  37,133,aur loot bhi unhi logon mein se tha jo rasool bana kar beje gay hain
  37,134,yaad karo jab hum ne is ko aur is ke sab ghar walon ko nijaat di
  37,135,siwaye aik budiya ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein se thi
  37,136,phir baqi sab ko tehass nehass kar diya
  37,137,aaj tum shab o roz unn ke ujre deyaar par se guzarte ho
  37,138,kya tum ko aqal nahi aati ?
  37,139,aur yaqeenan Younis bhi Rasolo-n mein se tha
  37,140,yaad karo jab woh aik bhari kashti ki taraf bhaag nikla
  37,141,phir quraa andazi mein shareek howa aur is mein maat khayi
  37,142,aakhir kaar machhli ne usay nigal liya aur woh malamat zada tha
  37,143,ab agar woh tasbeeh karne walon mein se nah hota to
  37,144,roz qayamat taq isi machhli ke pait mein rehta
  37,145,aakhir kaar hum ne usay barri saqeem haalat mein aik chtyal zameen par pheink diya
  37,146,aur uss par aik bail daar darakht uga diya
  37,147,"is ke baad hum ne ussay aik laakh, ya is se zayed logon ki taraf bheja"
  37,148,woh imaan laaye aur hum ne aik waqt khaas taq inhen baqi rakha
  37,149,"phir zara inn logon se pucho, kya ( inn ke dil ko yeh baat lagti hai ke ) tumahray rab ke liye to hon betiyan aur un ke liye hon betay !"
  37,150,kya waqai hum ne mulaika ko aurtain hi bana ya hai aur yeh aankhon dekhi baat keh rahay hain ?
  37,151,"khoob sun rakho, darasal yeh log apni mann gharat se yeh baat kehte hain"
  37,152,"ke Allah aulaad rakhta hai, aur fi al waqea yeh jhutay hain"
  37,153,kya Allah ne beiton ke bajaye betiyan apne liye pasand kar len ?
  37,154,"tumhe kya ho gaya hai, kaisay hukum laga rahay ho"
  37,155,kya tumhe hosh nahi aata
  37,156,ya phir tumahray paas apni un baton ke liye koi saaf sanad hai
  37,157,to lao apni woh kitaab agar tum sachey ho
  37,158,"unhon ne Allah aur mulaika ke darmain nasb ka rishta bana rakha hai, halaank mulaika khoob jantay hain ke yeh log mujrim ki hesiyat se paish honay walay hain"
  37,159,"( aur woh kehte hain ke )"" Allah unn sifaat se pak hai"
  37,160,jo uss ke khalis bundon ke siwa dosray log is ki taraf mansoob karte hain
  37,161,pas tum aur tumahray yeh mabood
  37,162,Allah se kisi ko phair nahi satke
  37,163,magar sirf uss ko jo dozakh ki bharakti hui aag mein jhlsne wala ho
  37,164,aur hamara haal to yeh hai ke hum mein se har aik ka aik maqam muqarrar hai
  37,165,aur hum saf basta khidmat gaar hain
  37,166,"aur tasbeeh karne walay hain """
  37,167,yeh log pehlay to kaha karte thay
  37,168,"ke kash hamaray paas woh"" zikar"" hota jo pichli qomon ko mila tha"
  37,169,to hum Allah ke cheeda bande hotay
  37,170,magar ( jab woh aa gaya ) to unhon ne is ka inkaar kar diya ab anqareeb aِnhin ( iss rawish ka nateeja ) maloom ho jaye ga
  37,171,apne beje hue bundon se hum pehlay hi wada kar chuke hain
  37,172,ke yaqeenan un ki madad ki jaye gi
  37,173,aur hamara lashkar hi ghalib ho kar rahay ga
  37,174,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, zara kuch mddt taq inhen inn ke haal par chore do"
  37,175,"aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud bhi dekh len ge"
  37,176,kya yeh hamaray azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain ?
  37,177,jab woh inn ke sehan mein aa utre ga to woh din unn logon ke liye bohat bura ho ga jinhein mutnabba kya ja chuka hai
  37,178,bas zara aِnhin kuch muddat ke liye chore do
  37,179,"aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud dekh len ge"
  37,180,"pak hai tera rab, izzat ka maalik, unn tamam baton se jo yeh log bana rahay hain"
  37,181,aur salam hai mursaleen par
  37,182,aur saari tareef Allah Rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai
